response.overview: Stella Sterling is a reporter at The Star Newspaper. She is also Starlight City’s superheroine, Cosmic Girl. Stella Sterling is working at her office when she receives an alert about Dr. Havoc’s whereabouts. The evil scientist has a lab in Starlight City. Cosmic Girl is ready to bring him to justice.  However, Dr. Havoc has created a new device. It is the Virtue Warp Ray. It corrupts a person’s virtue. Dr. Havoc blasts Cosmic Girl with the Virtue Warp Ray!  The corruption from the Virtue Warp Ray interferes with Cosmic Girl’s duties. The superheroine attempts to arrest a tech thief. The corruption leads to public humiliation.
response.title: Cosmic Girl - Sexual Corruption
